            li
              a(href='/_ah/api/explorer') Google Cloud Endpoints API Explorer
            |                 
            li
              a(href='https://console.developers.google.com') Google Developers Console
    .container.theme-showcase(role='main')
      //
        Output from Endpoints API call.
      #outputAlert.alert.alert-success(style='visibility: collapse;')
      //
        A form that takes a text value and submits it to the Endpoint,
        access to the Endpoint is enabled once the client is loaded below.
      .jumbotron
        .row
          .col-lg-12
            h1 Hello, Endpoints!
            |                 
            p
              | Enter your name and press the button below to call your Google Cloud Endpoints
              | API.
            |                 
            form
              .input-group
                input#nameInput.form-control.input-lg(type='text', placeholder='Name')
                |                           
                span.input-group-btn
                  button#helloButton.btn.btn-default.btn-primary.btn-group.btn-lg(type='submit') Say &quot;Hello&quot; &raquo;
            |                 
            br
            |                 
            p
              | If you need step-by-step instructions for connecting your Android application to
              | this backend module, see 
              a(href='https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/gradle-appengine-templates/tree/master/HelloEndpoints')
                | &quot;App
                | Engine Java Endpoints Module&quot; template documentation
              | .
            |                 
            p
              small
                | For more information about Google App Engine for Java, check out the 
                a(href='https://developers.google.com/appengine/docs/java/')
                  | App Engine
                  | documentation
                | .
                br
                |                         To learn more about Google Cloud Endpoints, see 
                a(href='https://developers.google.com/appengine/docs/java/endpoints/')
                  | Cloud
                  | Endpoints documentation
                | .
                br
                |                         If you&apos;d like to access your generated Google Cloud Endpoints APIs directly,
                |                         see the 
                a(href='/_ah/api/explorer') Cloud Endpoints API Explorer
